data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Kingsley Creek subdivision! This stunning property boasts 4 bedrooms (all en-suite), 4.5 baths, and a 3-car garage, ensuring ample space for comfortable living. Step onto the screened-in lanai with an extended paver deck, perfect for entertaining or enjoying serene outdoor moments in your fenced-in yard. Safety and security are paramount with the Simply Safe whole house security system. Inside, the kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring quartz countertops, a Motion Sense faucet, an Aquasana water filter, and top-of-the-line GE Cafe gas stove and microwave/convection oven. Need versatility? An additional flex room awaits, ideal for an office or formal dining. Custom shelving in the large walk-in pantry, master bedroom closet, and laundry room provide ample storage solutions. Secondary water tap from JEA for irrigation and three sun tubes inside.
